name: AIO  Monitor
description: It's a slim and compact all-in-one desktop for ease and convenience with less cables and clutter, a stand for your cell phone, plus instant privacy and instant login features for better security; wireless keyboard and mouse included

name: Strix MotherBoard
description: Faster memory: 4 memory slots support dual-channel DDR4 memory up to 128GB, with ASUS OptiMem enabling higher memory frequencies and lower latency

name: Primo Cooling fan
description: Tilt head and 2 speed functionality, and with new frustration free packaging you'll be using your new fan as fast as you can open the box

name: MEK Casing
description: With a USB 3.1 Gen 2 compatible USB-C connector on the front panel, it's easier than ever to connect the latest smartphones, high-speed external storage, or the latest peripherals to your PC.

name: Ruiz KeyBoard
description: Our Silent Gaming Switches with anti-ghosting technology for keystroke precision are made from durable, low-friction material for near-silent use and performance

name: Apex HardDrive
description: Available in capacities from 1TB to 20TB. | 1As used for storage capacity, 1 GB = 1 billion bytes and 1 TB = one trillion bytes. Actual user capacity may be less depending on operating environment.
